keyFacts: The document is an email forwarding FBI 302 documents (investigative reports) related to the Epstein case.
The email indicates collaboration between the FBI and the US Attorney's Office in New York (USANYS) in April 2020.
Multiple 302 document attachments are referenced, suggesting a substantial volume of investigative material was being shared.
The correspondence is part of a series (email 2 of 3), indicating organized document transmission.
